  "remarks": "Pakistani passport number 665334 issued in Kuwait. Pakistani passport number 917739 issued in Pakistan on 8 Aug 1991 expired on 7 Aug 1996. Mother's name is Aminah Ahmad Sher al-Baloushi. In custody of the United States. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 25 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded\non 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 9 September 2003 (amended 16 May 2011, 6 Dec 2019).",
